name: conan
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "conan" %}
{% set version = "1.1.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "3453edc61559e4cb2d12f7d4dcfec8860ccb644dc2155b1aaccf25b6022039cc" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  entry_points:
    - conan=conans.conan:run
    - conan_server=conans.conan_server:run
    - conan_build_info=conans.build_info.command:run
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - pyjwt >=1.4.0,<2.0.0
    - requests >=2.7.0,<3.0.0
    - colorama >=0.3.3,<0.4.0
    - pyyaml >=3.11,<3.13.0
    - python-patch ==1.16
    - fasteners >=0.14.1
    - six >=1.10.0
    - python-node-semver ==0.2.0
    - distro >=1.0.2,<1.2.0  # [linux]
    - pylint >=1.8.1,<1.9.0
    - future ==0.16.0
    - pygments >=2.0,<3.0
    - astroid >=1.6,<1.7
    - bottle >=0.12.8,<0.13
    - pluginbase >=0.5,<1.0

test:
  imports:
    - conans
    - conans.build_info
    - conans.client
    - conans.client.build
    - conans.client.cmd
    - conans.client.conf
    - conans.client.generators
    - conans.client.rest
    - conans.client.store
    - conans.client.tools
    - conans.model
    - conans.search
    - conans.server
    - conans.server.conf
    - conans.server.crypto
    - conans.server.crypto.jwt
    - conans.server.rest
    - conans.server.rest.bottle_plugins
    - conans.server.rest.controllers
    - conans.server.service
    - conans.server.store
    - conans.test
    - conans.test.build_helpers
    - conans.test.command
    - conans.test.conan_api
    - conans.test.functional
    - conans.test.generators
    - conans.test.integration
    - conans.test.model
    - conans.test.remote
    - conans.test.server
    - conans.test.server.crypto
    - conans.test.server.service
    - conans.test.server.utils
    - conans.test.util
    - conans.test.utils
    - conans.util
  commands:
    - conan --help
    - conan_build_info --help

about:
  home: https://conan.io
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE.md'
  summary: Conan C/C++ package manager
  doc_url: http://docs.conan.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/conan-io/conan

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - windelbouwmanbosch
    - windelbouwman
    - abloemert
    - memsharded
